						<p>This inscription is in characters of the 9-10th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This hero-stone, engraved in Kannaḍa, record is highly damaged. It seems to mention a person named Maindemma. Vallava is referred to. Mention is made of a village named Kāṇḍeyur.</p>						

